## 🐳 Docker Images

This release is available as Docker images:

```bash
# Latest version
docker pull guidedtraffic/dex-operator:latest

# Specific version
docker pull guidedtraffic/dex-operator:{{version}}
```

## ⎈ Helm Chart

```bash
helm repo add dex-operator https://guided-traffic.github.io/dex-operator/
helm repo update
helm install dex-operator dex-operator/dex-operator --version {{version}}
```

